  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Ministers and officers have no vision\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Ramanya Maha Nikaya Deputy Leader Gatambe Rajopavanaramadhapati Kappetiyagoda Sirivimala Thero said that the ministers do not have proper vision and do not take advice from those who have vision.",
        "There is no order in the work. Messing up all the work. Anunahimi said that problems have arisen in the agriculture sector because people who have knowledge about this and have feelings about this are not consulted.",
        "This was said at the time of the visit of the officials of the All Ceylon Agricultural Consultants Federation regarding the destruction of 3 Yala Maha Kannas due to the problems that have arisen in the current agriculture sector and the proper availability of pesticides and fertilizers."
      ],
